---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 112
By: Jâmî
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Consummation of Desire
  - Life-Love=Love=Our Love for God
---
In every veil you see, the Divine Beauty is concealed, making every heart a
slave to him.  In love to Him the heart finds its life; in desire for Him,
the soul finds its happiness. The heart which loves a fair one here, though
it knows it not, is really His lover.
